Description_lang: Deploys a crawler mine which burrows into the ground near a player. When a burrowed mine is triggered by a player, it will fixate on that player until the mine comes within $262372R yards of a player. When it does, it will detonate, inflicting $262348s1 Fire damage instantly and $262348s2 Fire damage over $262348t2 sec for $262348d to all players within $262348A1 yards.
